ersality, which is based on the conceptual complementarity of the world (the given) and its creatures (the giving).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aPsychoanalysis. 4aPhilosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Metaphysics.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEdinburgh University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311078042040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781474450782?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781474450782423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781474450782/original  a978-3-11-078042-0  Edinburgh University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK